      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver, though it shows clear signs of its age. The exterior has several noticeable scratches, a few small dents, and the clear coat is beginning to peel on the roof and trunk. Inside, the upholstery shows significant wear and some staining, but all essential electronics and climate controls remain functional. Mechanically, the car starts reliably and handles well, though it may require minor maintenance items in the near future. It is a solid, budget-friendly option for someone looking for dependable transportation without the premium price of a newer model.",
