      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been well-maintained throughout its ownership. The engine runs smoothly and the transmission shifts as expected, providing a reliable and comfortable driving experience. While the exterior and interior show some minor signs of normal wear, such as small paint chips or light upholstery creasing, the car is mechanically sound and ready for the road. It has a clean title and up-to-date service records, making it a solid choice for anyone looking for a dependable pre-owned vehicle.",
